---
export const prerender = true;

import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About — Rabbit Holes" description="Learn about Rabbit Holes, a curiosity-driven blog exploring ideas worth tumbling down into.">
  <div class="about-container">
    <div class="page-header">
      <div class="page-label">About</div>
      <h1>Curating curiosity, one rabbit hole at a time</h1>
      <p class="page-intro">This is a place for ideas worth tumbling down into. Essays, links, and observations about the things that make us think differently.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
      <p>Rabbit Holes started as a simple question: What if we had a space dedicated not to quick takes and hot opinions, but to ideas that deserve time and attention?</p>

      <p>The internet is full of shallow browsing. Click, scan, move on. But the best ideas don't work that way. They require patience. They reveal themselves slowly. They connect to other ideas in unexpected ways.</p>

      <div class="quote-block">
        <blockquote>The cure for boredom is curiosity. There is no cure for curiosity.</blockquote>
        <cite>Dorothy Parker</cite>
      </div>

      <h2>What You'll Find Here</h2>

      <p>Essays exploring how we think, learn, and create. Links to ideas that deserve deeper attention. Observations about technology, culture, and the spaces between. Everything curated with one question: Is this worth your time?</p>

      <p>Not everything published here will resonate with everyone. That's by design. This isn't about mass appeal—it's about finding the ideas that matter to you, the ones that spark something, that make you see things differently.</p>

      <h2>On Curation</h2>

      <p>Curation is an act of care. It's saying: "I found this, thought about it, and believe it's worth sharing." In an age of algorithmic recommendations, human curation matters more than ever.</p>

      <p>The algorithms optimize for engagement. I optimize for meaning. Sometimes those align. Often they don't.</p>

      <h2>Why "Rabbit Holes"?</h2>

      <p>Because the best learning happens when you follow curiosity wherever it leads. When you click one link that leads to another, when you pick up a book referenced in an essay, when you discover connections nobody planned.</p>

      <p>This site is designed for that kind of exploration. Take your time. Follow the links. See where they lead.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="links-section">
      <h2>More Rabbit Holes</h2>
      <div class="links-grid">
        <a href="https://booktrails.rabbitholes.garden" class="link-card">
          <h3>Book Trails</h3>
          <p>Curated reading paths through ideas and genres</p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://papertrails.rabbitholes.garden" class="link-card">
          <h3>Paper Trails</h3>
          <p>Academic papers and research worth exploring</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-section">
      <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
      <p>Have a link worth sharing? An idea to explore? Found something broken?</p>
      <p>Email: <a href="mailto:bhuvan@bebhuvan.com">bhuvan@bebhuvan.com</a></p>
      <p>Or find me on <a href="https://twitter.com/bebhuvan" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Twitter</a> where I share works-in-progress and interesting finds.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .about-container {
      max-width: var(--width-content);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 80px 40px 120px;
    }

    .page-header {
      margin-bottom: 80px;
      padding-bottom: 80px;
      border-bottom: 3px solid var(--color-text-primary);
    }

    .page-label {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--color-text-light);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-size: 52px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      color: var(--color-text-primary);
    }

    .page-intro {
      font-size: 24px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .about-content {
      font-size: 22px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    }

    .about-content p {
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .about-content p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .about-content h2 {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.3;
      margin-top: 80px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      letter-spacing: -0.018em;
      color: var(--color-text-primary);
    }

    .about-content h2:first-child {
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    .quote-block {
      margin: 80px 0;
      padding: 48px 0 48px 56px;
      border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(232, 118, 83, 0.02) 0%, transparent 100%);
    }

    .quote-block blockquote {
      font-family: 'Crimson Pro', serif;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .quote-block cite {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-style: normal;
      color: var(--color-text-light);
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .quote-block cite::before {
      content: '— ';
      color: var(--color-accent);
    }

    .links-section {
      margin-top: 80px;
      padding-top: 60px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
    }

    .links-section h2 {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--color-accent);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .links-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .link-card {
      padding: 24px;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: block;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }

    .link-card:hover {
      border-color: var(--color-accent);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .link-card h3 {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--color-text-primary);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .link-card p {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
      margin: 0;
    }

    .contact-section {
      margin-top: 80px;
      padding: 48px;
      background: var(--color-off-white);
      border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
    }

    .contact-section h2 {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--color-text-primary);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .contact-section p {
      font-size: 19px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .contact-section p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .contact-section a {
      color: var(--color-accent);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .contact-section a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .about-container {
        padding: 60px 24px 80px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 36px;
      }

      .page-header {
        margin-bottom: 60px;
        padding-bottom: 60px;
      }

      .page-intro {
        font-size: 20px;
      }

      .about-content {
        font-size: 20px;
      }

      .about-content h2 {
        font-size: 28px;
        margin-top: 60px;
      }

      .quote-block {
        margin: 60px 0;
        padding: 36px 0 36px 40px;
      }

      .quote-block blockquote {
        font-size: 24px;
      }

      .links-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .contact-section {
        padding: 32px 24px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Base>
